      <title>飓风在温暖水域加速袭击佛罗里达</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/hurricane-slams-florida-after-picking-up-speed-in-warm-waters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风黛比在温暖的水域中增强后，以一级飓风的形式袭击了佛罗里达州塔拉哈西东南部，这是本季节将是热带气旋多发季节的最新证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/hurricane-slams-florida-after-picking-up-speed-in-warm-waters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 11:07:23 GMT</pubDate>
