      <title>瑞银金塞拉称美联储本周不太可能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/ubp-s-kinsella-says-fed-cut-unlikely-this-week-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合私人银行外汇策略全球主管彼得·金塞拉认为，美联储本周没有必要降息。他告诉彭博电视台，美联储在会议间隙降息将向“市场发出恐慌信号”。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/ubp-s-kinsella-says-fed-cut-unlikely-this-week-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 10:40:51 GMT</pubDate>
